ar throughout Christendom, in part because St Thomas's doubts have made him seem a very human character."],"variants":[]}],"historicEvents":[{"id":1705193,"age":2,"year":"1337","toYear":"1453","julianDay":2209390,"title":"The Hundred Years' War","description":"The Hundred Years' War between France and England was largely due to the question of legitimate succession to the French crown.","jurisdictionLevel":2}],"lifeSummary":"Thomas Power was born in 1335, in London, Middlesex, England. He married Eleanor Power about 1360. They were the parents of at least 1 daughter. He died in 1364, in his hometown, at the age of 29."},"et":{"1335–1364":"1335–1364","1340–1410":"1340–1410","1365–1464":"1365–1464","about 1360":"umbes 1360","1337":"1337","1335":"1335","1410":"1410","1453":"1453","1464":"1464","1365":"1365","1364":"1364","1340":"1340","London Middlesex England":"London, Middlesex, England"},"fi":{"1335–1364":"1335–1364","1340–1410":"1340–1410","1365–1464":"1365–1464","about 1360":"noin 1360","1337":"1337","1335":"1335","1410":"1410","1453":"1453","1464":"1464","1365":"1365","1364":"1364","1340":"1340","London Middlesex England":"London, Middlesex, England"},"fr":{"1335–1364":"1335–1364","1340–1410":"1340–1410","1365–1464":"1365–1464","about 1360":"environ 1360","1337":"1337","1335":"1335","1410":"1410","1453":"1453","1464":"1464","1365":"1365","1364":"1364","1340":"1340","London Middlesex England":"Londres, Middlesex, Angleterre","lifeSummary":"Thomas Power est né en 1335, à Londres, Middlesex, Angleterre. Il a épousé Eleanor Power environ 1360. Ils ont eu au moins 1 fille. Il est décédé en 1364, dans sa ville natale, à l’âge de 29 ans."},"de":{"1335–1364":"1335–1364","1340–1410":"1340–1410","1365–1464":"1365–1464","about 1360":"um 1360","1337":"1337","1335":"1335","1410":"1410","1453":"1453","1464":"1464","1365":"1365","1364":"1364","1340":"1340","London Middlesex England":"London, Middlesex, England","lifeSummary":"Thomas Power wurde 1335 in London, Middlesex, Englan